#: ckan/templates/admin/config.html:51
#, python-format
msgid ""
"<p><strong>Site Title:</strong> This is the title of this CKAN instance It "
"appears in various places throughout CKAN.</p> <p><strong>Custom "
"Stylesheet:</strong> Define an alternative main CSS file.</p> "
"<p><strong>Site Tag Logo:</strong> This is the logo that appears in the "
"header of all the CKAN instance templates.</p> <p><strong>About:</strong> "
"This text will appear on this CKAN instances <a href=\"%(about_url)s\">about"
" page</a>.</p> <p><strong>Intro Text:</strong> This text will appear on this"
" CKAN instances <a href=\"%(home_url)s\">home page</a> as a welcome to "
"visitors.</p> <p><strong>Custom CSS:</strong> This is a block of CSS that "
"appears in <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> tag of every page. If you wish to "
"customize the templates more fully we recommend <a href=\"%(docs_url)s\" "
"target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">reading the documentation</a>.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p><strong>站台標題：</strong>此 CKAN 網站的標題，將顯示於全站當中的各種地方。</p> "
"<p><strong>自訂樣式表：</strong>指定替代的主 CSS 檔案位置。</p> "
"<p><strong>站台圖示：</strong>這是會出現在所有 CKAN 頁面範本頂端的網站圖示。</p> "
"<p><strong>關於：</strong>此文字將顯示於此 CKAN 系統的<a "
"href=\"%(about_url)s\">關於頁面</a>當中。</p> <p><strong>簡介文字：</strong>此文字將顯示於此 "
"CKAN 系統的<a href=\"%(home_url)s\">首頁當中</a>，用於歡迎造訪者。</p> <p><strong>自訂 "
"CSS：</strong>這個段落的 CSS 會插入到每一頁頂端的 <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> "
"標籤當中。若您想要更完整地自訂頁面範本，我們建議先<a href=\"%(docs_url)s\" target=\"_blank\" "
"rel=\"noreferrer\">閱讀過文件再動手</a>。</p> "
"<p><strong>首頁：</strong>此選項可用來選擇要在首頁顯示的預設功能模組與版面。</p>"

