"already been created for you with the username %(user_name)s. You can change"
" it later. You have been added to the %(group_type)s %(group_title)s with "
"the following role: %(role_name)s. To accept this invite, please reset your "
"password at: %(reset_link)s Have a nice day. -- Message sent by "
"%(site_title)s (%(site_url)s)"
