#: ckan/templates/home/index.html:3
msgid "Welcome"
msgstr "歡迎"

#: ckan/templates/home/snippets/about_text.html:1
msgid ""
"<p>CKAN is the world’s leading open-source data portal platform.</p> <p>CKAN"
" is a complete out-of-the-box software solution that makes data accessible "
"and usable – by providing tools to streamline publishing, sharing, finding "
"and using data (including storage of data and provision of robust data "
"APIs). CKAN is aimed at data publishers (national and regional governments, "
"companies and organizations) wanting to make their data open and "
"available.</p> <p>CKAN is used by governments and user groups worldwide and "
"powers a variety of official and community data portals including portals "
"for local, national and international government, such as the UK’s <a "
"href=\"https://data.gov.uk\">data.gov.uk</a> and the United States <a "
"href=\"https://catalog.data.gov/\">catalog.data.gov</a>, the Brazilian <a "
"href=\"https://dados.gov.br/\">dados.gov.br</a>, Dutch and Netherland "
"government portals, as well as city and municipal sites in the US, UK, "
"Argentina, Finland and elsewhere.</p> <p>CKAN: <a "
"href=\"https://ckan.org/\">https://ckan.org/</a><br /> CKAN Showcases: <a "
"href=\"https://ckan.org/showcase\">https://ckan.org/showcase</a><br /> "
"Features overview: <a "
"href=\"https://ckan.org/features/\">https://ckan.org/features/</a></p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>CKAN 是世界領先的開放原始碼資料入口網站平台。</p> <p>CKAN "
"提供了讓發布、分享、尋找、使用各類數據資料更加便利的工具，更包含資料儲存空間與完善的 "
"API，是一套完全開箱即用的軟體解決方案，讓資料可供大眾存取使用。CKAN "
"是針對希望讓資料能夠開放，讓任何人都能使用的資料發布者（全國性或地方政府、企業、組織）所設計的。</p> <p>全球的不同國家政府、使用者群組使用 "
"CKAN，提供各種官方與社群性質開放資料入口網站，諸如英國的 <a "
"href=\"https://data.gov.uk\">data.gov.uk</a>、美國的 <a "
"href=\"https://catalog.data.gov/\">catalog.data.gov</a>、巴西的 <a "
"href=\"https://dados.gov.br/\">dados.gov.br</a>、荷蘭的政府資料入口網站，還有美國、英國、阿根廷、芬蘭與其他國家的多個城市所提供的資料網站。</p>"
" <p>CKAN：<a href=\"https://ckan.org/\">https://ckan.org/</a><br />CKAN "
"案例展示：<a href=\"https://ckan.org/showcase\">https://ckan.org/showcase</a><br "
"/>功能概觀：<a "
"href=\"https://ckan.org/features/\">https://ckan.org/features/</a></p>"

